reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater comfortable, soft, and well-made, appreciating its feminine look and dark green color options. The fit receives positive feedback, with one customer noting it hits at the hip bone, while others mention the sleeves don't hang over their hands. The length receives mixed reviews, with several customers noting it's shorter than expected.

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice!
items.body: Nice quality sweater with a nicely done design. Should have sized up, but then sleeves would be too long for my arms. Comfortable. Looks nice. Won't know how durable it is until it gets washed a few times I do recommend it. Read more
items.author: Laurie

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Order one to two sizes larger if you don't want a close-fitting, short-towards waist sweater
items.body: This sweater is attractive, but I wish I'd ordered a size or 2 larger, as it is closer-fitting & shorter than I'd expected. It feels more "cottony" than most sweaters I've bought lately, but the design is very nice. Read more
items.author: Shelley

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Like this sweater but not the top
items.body: I like this sweater overall but do not like how the stitching sticks out on the top and looks like shorty work. Overall it fits nice and is comfortable but this is disappointing to me because I can’t hide it from showing and so I had to take it to my tailor to fix Read more
items.author: CUSTOMER

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great item. Thanks.
items.author: WAYNE FORRESTER

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars A size up for cozy loose!
items.body: I originally ordered as per size chart (mfg and Amazon recommended size, large) had to return and order size up. (Extra Large) This sweater is BEAUTIFUL! BEAUTIFUL FIT (one size up, for me, not too tight, but super cozy) BEAUTIFUL MATERIAL so soft, smooth, not Itchy or Scratchy *calm down (insert known animated series here), fans! I now own 4 of these sweaters in different colors (unlike favorite *same animated series*, characters), I Absolutely Love Them! I highly recommend *one size up, if you like your sweaters not 'binding-feeling'. Just a little loose and cozy. I can layer a tank or tshirt under, if I want, and still use a warm winter coat over all of it. I love the neck line.. not quite a turtleneck, but close enough to me warm, but not choking. I love that I feel very comfortable wearing these with my comfy sports bras, yet still feel and look very well put together! 5 stars for this BEAUTIFUL sweater! I might take away for size inaccuracy. We need better size charts for selling "Normal US Sizes"! Getting so annoying! I'm never confident in a new clothing purchases because of the discrepancies between sizing from different manufacturers. Read more
items.author: That Girl

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Muy desilusionada.
items.body: El sweater tiene la trama muy abierta, nada que ver con la imagen que se ofrece del producto. Si bien es 100%acrilico, el aspecto es muy como “de plástico” y no creo que abrigue mucho ya que el tejido es mucho más abierto de lo que se ve en la foto. Lamentablemente no puedo devolverlo porque lo encargué a Uruguay y ya no puedo hacer la devolución . Además tiene aspecto que se va a estirar, por la trama tan floja y abierta del tejido. Me siento ESTAFADA porque además compré “off white” y llegó uno blanco blanco!! No lo usaré. No me gusta nada. Eso no vale el dinero que pagué. Read more
items.author: Laura Alfonso

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: F Blue, Fen Green, Light Coffee, Zh Blue, Xian Green, Army Green, Xian M Red, 01xian Red, Orange, Beige, Lian Purple, Light Pink, Purple Blue, Rust Red. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
